com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui

Class Icon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.UIObject
      • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget
        • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.Icon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasAlignment, HasAttachHandlers, HasHandlers, EventListener, HasVisibility, IsWidget

    public class Icon
extends Widget
implements HasAlignment
    Widget with a black or white icon.

    The icons are provided by Glyphicons and Font Awesome.

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:Icon type="PLANE" />

    Since:
    2.0.4.0
    Author:
    Carlos Alexandro Becker, Dominik Mayer, Sven Jacobs
    See Also:
    IconStack, Bootstrap documentation, Font Awesome page
